description: Under normal circumstances, the fund invests its net assets in equity securities included in a portfolio of 500 large cap U.S. companies weighted by market capitalization, ETFs that invest in or track the performance of such large cap U.S. companies, financial instruments, such as swap agreements, futures contracts and other financial instruments that provide daily exposure to such large cap U.S. companies.
name: NightShares 500 1x/1.5x ETF
